Description: lightning-fast ASGI server (Avalan PPA pin)
 uvicorn is an ASGI web server, built on uvloop and httptools, with
 first-class HTTP/1.1 and WebSocket support. This rebuild pins 0.35.0
 because Avalan tracks >= 0.35, < 0.36 and Debian sid carries 0.38.x
 (above the ceiling). The lightweight install profile is built here;
 uvicorn's optional `[standard]` extra (httptools, uvloop, watchfiles,
 websockets, PyYAML, python-dotenv) is left to whatever those Noble
 packages provide and not pulled in by this rebuild's Depends.
